{"tid":479943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"收租客沽騰訊 2400萬買三間樓","createTime":"2017-11-25T15:42:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-26T07:52:33.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0ee1f12761005c0e2a45e1e27607fa9b0e2e5dfb","tid":479943,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"【匯璽II開售】收租客沽騰訊 2400萬買三間樓 <br />\n<br />\n居住在火炭的投資者黃先生表示，自己是匯璽I 向隅客，之前入票4次都抽唔到，今次終於抽到，但抽籤唔辛苦，喺早起身排隊先辛苦，但他強調，喺新地樓先買。<br />\n他透露，自己是套現股票轉投樓市，直言磚頭保值過股票。是次斥資2400萬，買入3個1伙單位，其中1間是用家人的首置身份，省去15%的辣稅。他續指，2間打算用來收租，預計每間月租約2萬元，而另1間就畀個19歲仔。<br />\n記者問到有冇買股王騰訊(700)，黃生指只是賺少少就走了，「我股票賣左啦，咪投資呢啲囉(今次係套股換樓?)」<br />\n他感嘆，現時樓價貴，都唔知現時入市啱定錯，但都相信樓市唔會大跌，最多跌少少。他透露，自己在西九龍有數間物業收租。<br />\n記者︰葉煜燊<br />\n蘋果財經，關心你飯碗<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=LbU%2BMhBpAYBXBUYqnlzIeJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=7161f10c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171125/57503411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171125%2F57503411&d=LbU%2BMhBpAYBXBUYqnlzIeJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8554d5e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171125%2F57503411&h=a1d1b606\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171125/57503411</a>"},{"pid":"5db4a5590177891a31de23c0adc927102a6f63c1","tid":479943,"uid":116718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"敢all in磚頭唔敢all in股票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb541dc63a1bca86cf5275cba3931aeafe55151c","tid":479943,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T15:48:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/n